@startuml
autonumber
skinparam BoxPadding 10

actor "OPC-UA Server" as Server
box "Ingest Service (Python)" #LightBlue
    participant "Ingest Main" as Ingest
    participant "DataProcessor" as Processor
    participant "DatabaseManager" as DB
    participant "MqttManager" as MQTT
end box
database "TimescaleDB" as Timescale
queue "MQTT Broker" as Broker

== Path 1: Telemetry Data Ingestion (Boolean / Numeric) ==
Server -> Ingest: DataChange (raw_value: True / 23.5)
activate Ingest
Ingest -> Processor: process(raw_value)
activate Processor
note over Processor
  **Value Normalization Logic:**
  - If boolean (True/False) -> Cast to float (1.0 / 0.0)
  - If integer/float (23.5) -> Cast to float (23.5)
end note
Processor --> Ingest: SensorData(value=1.0, hot_path=True)
deactivate Processor

Ingest -> DB: insert(SensorData, "laser_data")
activate DB
DB -> Timescale: INSERT INTO laser_data (value=1.0)
deactivate DB

alt if hot_path == True
    Ingest -> MQTT: publish(SensorData, "laser_01")
    activate MQTT
    MQTT -> Broker: Topic: factory/laser_01/IsConnected\nPayload: {"timestamp": "...", "value": 1.0}
    deactivate MQTT
end
deactivate Ingest

== Path 2: Event Data Ingestion (Text / Strings) ==
Server -> Ingest: DataChange (raw_value: "Vacuum Failure")
activate Ingest
Ingest -> Processor: process(raw_value)
activate Processor
note over Processor
  **Value Normalization Logic:**
  - If string ("Vacuum Failure") and non-numeric -> Keep as string
end note
Processor --> Ingest: SensorData(value="Vacuum Failure", hot_path=True)
deactivate Processor

Ingest -> DB: insert(SensorData, "delta_robot_data")
activate DB
note over DB
  **Dynamic Table Routing:**
  - If isinstance(value, str):
    Redirect query from 'delta_robot_data' to 'machine_events'
end note
DB -> Timescale: INSERT INTO machine_events (message="Vacuum Failure")
deactivate DB
deactivate Ingest
@enduml